<span class="comment"><font color=#000000>I agree that the conversations are difficult. When I click the notification window to see a reply, all I get is that one reply. I find it cumbersome to find the full conversation, to the point where I usually go to that person's page and find the original, eschewing the notifications altogether.</font></span><p><font size=1><u><a href="reply?id=3827777&whence=%69%74%65%6d%3f%69%64%3d%33%38%32%37%34%30%36">reply</a></u></font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td><table border=0><tr><td><img src="http://ycombinator.com/images/s.gif" height=1 width=80></td><td valign=top><center><a id=up_3828024 href="vote?for=3828024&dir=up&whence=%69%74%65%6d%3f%69%64%3d%33%38%32%37%34%30%36"><img src="http://ycombinator.com/images/grayarrow.gif" border=0 vspace=3 hspace=2></a><span id=down_3828024></span></center></td><td class="default"><div style="margin-top:2px; margin-bottom:-10px; "><span class="comhead"><a href="user?id=jmillikin">jmillikin</a> 18 hours ago  | <a href="item?id=3828024">link</a></span></div><br>
